A video has emerged showing two men seemingly beating a Vaal Rand Flying Squad police officer, Chiny Mareka, 42, at KFC Vaal Mall on the East Rand on Thursday. In the video captured on Wednesday, the man is seen running into the store, grabbing a chair in apparent self-defence when he was beaten up by two men. More people are seen getting in trying to intervene. Mareka has since laid charges of assault against the two males with the Vanderbijlpark Police Station, Sedibeng Ster reported. More details to follow. &#8211; Caxton News Service For more news your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter .